lenders.name: Dow
lenders.loan_because:
There are few ways for those with roughly adequate resources to help those with very limited resources.  Kiva corrects that and allows someone like me who is comfortable but not wealthy, to make a difference.  
I also love cutting banks out of the loan process.  Community decides which projects get funded and wealthy entities don't get to skim off vulnerable populations or those putting in the hard work.
lenders.occupational_info: I'm a writer, an out trans activist, a single parent (and loads of other weird stuff) and I work for a start-up, myself.  So, I champion Kiva's spirit, know the challenges and sense of accomplishment that surviving and thriving quarter after quarter brings.  Shine on, Kiva.
